"Filter-order range, ``order_hi`` exclusive. Defaults to ``range(2, 42)`` "
"→ 40 orders."
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.config.SweepConfig:31 of
msgid "Number of cutoff frequencies sampled linearly in ``(0, 1)``."
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.config.SweepConfig:37 of
msgid "Default selections when no CLI override is given."
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.config.SweepConfig:41 of
msgid ""
"Output locations. The ``.npz`` checkpoints live under ``data/sweeps`` and"
" are versioned; the figures under ``figures/sweeps`` are derived from "
"those checkpoints."
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.config.SweepConfig:47 of
